{"tid":163352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾hkdryclub狗也不屌","createTime":"2017-03-20T02:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T07:00:45.000Z","uid":52210,"like":385,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50889699742a539abf1046eb8a052e94fd03deec","tid":163352,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:04:23.000Z","msg":"我都忍左個垃圾mk page好耐<br />\n偷完人圖或者片唔落credit都算<br />\n最近仲要落埋自己所謂studio既logo<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/094835_7b8d9103354113ab118992c3542a0dec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F094835_7b8d9103354113ab118992c3542a0dec.jpg&h=a6e97945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下做乜撚野？<br />\n你呢個垃圾studio參與左條片製作既邊部分？<br />\n加d字上去就變你成品？<br />\n比埋原片你睇<br />\n費事有d盲既護主犬話條animation真係佢地整<br />\n原片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R1vnFfTaLAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR1vnFfTaLAA&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d41bd2f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R1vnFfTaLAA</a><br />\n<br />\n好心呢d垃圾page就快d執柒左佢啦<br />\nd mk admin間唔時就po一兩句冇意思既野叫春<br />\n係咪以為自己好型呀<br />\n好呢個我算 可能d mk admin真係好撚型<br />\n<br />\n講翻最近年宵佢地賣個件 I am A0 tee<br />\n屌你老味柒撚到仆街<br />\n完全冇美感可言都擺出街賣<br />\n件tee又冇意思又柒<br />\n都可以賣到咁好生意<br />\n睇下宜家有邊個會著出街？<br />\n其他檔比心機設計賣貴少少又比香港人屌<br />\n好 你會話呢d係marketing冇得怨<br />\n<br />\n但其實講到尾我想鬧既係宜家d香港人<br />\n人地偷圖偷片你地仲附和<br />\n好似冇問題咁<br />\n其他studio雖然作品柒柒地<br />\n但起碼用心製作<br />\n<br />\n想講既係宜家香港人愈黎愈冇要求同品味<br />\n當呢d垃圾mk食女page都可以咁多人follow既時候<br />\n香港人已經慢慢變成大陸人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb9c2de4ec9f957b937cb566909473e19b9c8de","tid":163352,"uid":69095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:06:15.000Z","msg":"海關好似唔知wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7be68f79361cce3b